HEADWORD: Rundel
<hw>Run"del</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Rindle</er>.]</ety> <def>A moat with water in it; also, a small
stream; a runlet.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>
